Create Folder Structure in your Computer (This is for organising your Projects/ E-Content)

E:/   (C or D Drive)
analytics
projects
ebooks
datasets
download


We will organise all our analytics work in these folders. If you don’t have E drive, use C or D drives
projects - save our repositories (all codes in folders)
ebooks - all reference books/ cheat sheets
datasets - all sample datasets from various sources
Download - here you can save all your setup files - anaconda, git, git desktop etc


